# Monorepo — Shooting Challenge

## Scope

This repo (`127-si-shooting-challenge`) is **Shooting Challenge only**:

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `airtable/automations/shooting-challenge/` | Production Airtable automation scripts (numbered `001`–`114`) |
| `airtable/extension-scripts/audits/` | Dry-run pipeline audits (Stages A–J) |
| `airtable/extension-scripts/safe-backfills/` | Controlled repair/backfill extensions |
| `airtable/schema/` | Schema notes + dated snapshots |
| `web/` | Next.js app — deployed at **`/shoot`** on hoopchallenges.com |
| `make/` | Make.com blueprints and upload/email docs |
| `tools/airtable/` | Python schema export CLI |
| `media/` | Season publicity assets (newspapers, radio, social) — see [media/README.md](../media/README.md) |
| `docs/` | Ops docs — **start at `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md`** |

**Not in this repo:** Hoop landing (`hoopchallenges-landing`), JR Ref (`127-si-jr-ref`).

## AI session startup

1. Read [docs/v2/04-ai-development-standards.md](../docs/v2/04-ai-development-standards.md) — **Task Classification + Workspace Check** on every new task; redirect if Mike is in wrong phase/tool/repo.
2. Read `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md` for live base IDs, audit status, Vercel settings.
3. Use `docs/README.md` to find the right doc.
4. For automations → `docs/automation-index.md` + `.cursor/rules/airtable-automation-scripts.mdc`.
5. For web routes → `web/docs/site-hierarchy.md` + `.cursor/rules/web-ui-brand.mdc`.

**Wrong area redirects (Cursor):** Planning/copy/review → ChatGPT. Code/audits/commits without approved backlog ID → stop first. Backlog → `docs/v2-change-backlog.md` only. Not this repo: `hoopchallenges-landing`, `127-si-jr-ref`.

## Deploy paths

| Target | Workflow |
|--------|----------|
| **Airtable** | Edit `airtable/automations/shooting-challenge/*.js` → commit → paste into Airtable automation (skip GitHub header) |
| **Vercel** | Push `master`; project Root Directory = `web`; env vars in Vercel dashboard |
| **Make** | Export blueprint to `make/blueprints/`; document in `make/documentation/` |

## Secrets

Never commit or log: `AIRTABLE_API_TOKEN`, `.env`, `.env.local`, Make webhook secrets.

## Changelog

Production-impacting changes → `CHANGELOG.md` under `### Airtable`, `### Web`, or `### Make`.
